		<description><![CDATA[This is the method they used at IUC in Yokohama. They would literally pound us with article after article on the same topic until we had all the vocab and could discuss it without trouble. It really works when it&#039;s coming at you day after day.

That&#039;s another reason why translators specialize in one subject!

Good stuff.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This is the method they used at IUC in Yokohama. They would literally pound us with article after article on the same topic until we had all the vocab and could discuss it without trouble. It really works when it&#8217;s coming at you day after day.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s another reason why translators specialize in one subject!</p>
<p>Good stuff.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
